                                                               <font>
                                                                  <Font name="MS Outlook" size="15.0" />
                                                               </font>
                                                            </TitledPane>
                                                         </children>
                                                      </AnchorPane>
                                                    <AnchorPane minHeight="0.0" minWidth="0.0" prefHeight="135.0" prefWidth="497.0">
                                                         <children>
                                                            <TitledPane alignment="TOP_CENTER" collapsible="false" prefHeight="271.0" prefWidth="511.0" text="DIFENSORE" textAlignment="CENTER" textFill="#200af5" AnchorPane.bottomAnchor="0.0" AnchorPane.leftAnchor="0.0" AnchorPane.rightAnchor="0.0" AnchorPane.topAnchor="0.0">
                                                               <content>
                                                                  <AnchorPane minHeight="0.0" minWidth="0.0" prefHeight="107.0" prefWidth="481.0">
                                                                     <children>
                                                                        <TextArea editable="false" layoutY="1.0" prefHeight="243.0" prefWidth="509.0" text="&#10;Il difensore, a sua volta, lancia tanti dadi quante sono le sue&#10;armate presenti sul territorio per un massimo di 3 dadi (blu).&#10;&#10;Il difensore deve dichiarare&#10;con quante armate intende combattere prima che&#10;l’attaccante abbia lanciato i dadi.&#10;" AnchorPane.bottomAnchor="-12.0" AnchorPane.leftAnchor="-12.0" AnchorPane.rightAnchor="-12.0" AnchorPane.topAnchor="-12.0">
                                                                           <font>
                                                                              <Font name="MS Outlook" size="14.0" />
                                                                           </font>
                                                                        </TextArea>
